summary:
Currently on secondment from PwC Australia to PwC Netherlands. I am a manager in the international tax team of PwC Netherlands and have a key focus on sustainability and environmental taxes. I have a keen interest in the pricing of carbon and how economics interacts with environmental outcomes and policies. 

I am passionate about community, inclusion and diversity and the impact we have on each other and the planet.
